SUMMARY:OCEAN SLEEPER (AUS) / HOPSYDIAN (IT) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Chelsea
DESCRIPTION: Hailing from regional Victoria\, Australia\, Ocean Sleeper have been carving their name into the metalcore scene with raw emotion\, crushing breakdowns\, and soaring melodic hooks. Since their formation in 2016\, the band has built a loyal following at home and abroad\, delivering powerful records and unforgettable live shows that speak to the heart of modern heavy music. With their acclaimed debut album Don’t Leave Me This Way and 2025 EP Maybe Death Is All I Need\, Ocean Sleeper cemented their place as one of Australia’s most exciting heavy acts and now move on to tackling the rest of the world. Their sound bridges brutal intensity and emotional vulnerability—drawing comparisons to genre heavyweights while forging a voice uniquely their own. 2025 saw the band fully sell out their second Australian headline tour in a Row\, Hit the United states for the first time and headlining\, and finished the year in Europe and United Kingdom for the first time.  2026 has already shown they are not slowing down! 3 festivals across Australia with Polaris\, We Came As Romans\, touring Japan with UK legends caskets and now returning to Europe UK supporting Nevertel and a select amount of headline shows due to huge demand.  The band has supported tours with While She Sleeps\, Make Them Suffer\, Stick To Your Guns\, brought amazing bands to support them in Australia like Point North\, Lil Lotus to Thousand Below\, as well as landed festivals with Limp Bizkit\, Fall Out boy and more! Prepare for a night of raw power and honest emotion. Ocean Sleeper is ready to show Europe and the UK what Australian metalcore is all about.   www.oceansleeper.com www.instagram.com/oceansleeper www.facebook.com/oceansleeper   Support: HOPSYDIAN www.instagram.com/hopsydianofficial/?hl=de   Tickets: www.oeticket.com/event/21410163?affiliate=MT5
URL:https://www.chelsea.co.at/concerts.php#concert_6650
